	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The central Halogen component. Manages the graph canvas, controls (depth/fit/tours), search box, and detail sidebar. Holds the full application state: selected node, hovered elements, search results, tutorial progress, and prompt input. All user interaction flows through Viewer's action handlers." ;
